casebody.data:
Certiorari Denied.

No. 628. Commerce Company v. United States. Ben Connolly for petitioner. Solicitor General Perlman, Assistant Attorney General Caudle, Ellis N. Slack and Lee A. Jackson for the United States. William A. Sutherland filed a brief, as amicus curiae, supporting the petition.

C. A. 5th Cir. Certiorari denied.
